  • Method Details

    • getMappingsVersion

      public static String getMappingsVersion(Server server)
      Get the version of the mappings used by CraftBukkit. Note that this method only works on (forks of) CraftBukkit.
      Parameters:
      server - the Server instance
      Returns:
      the mappings version (may be used for equality checking only), or null if running on CraftBukkit 1.13.2 or earlier.
      Note:
      org.bukkit.craftbukkit.util.CraftMagicNumbers#getMappingsVersion() was only introduced at CraftBukkit 1.14
